---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { u } from '../utils/url';
---

<Layout title="Testimonials" description="What clients say about P.K. Gills Aquatics and Pat Ann Church. Testimonials from aquatics companies, CPAs, and water conservation districts.">

  <section class="py-16" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #041e35, #063356);">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <nav class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm mb-6" style="color: #6ec2f7;">
        <a href={u("/")} style="color: #a8dbfb;" class="hover:text-white">Home</a>
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 opacity-50" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        <span>Testimonials</span>
      </nav>
      <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-white text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-4">Testimonials</h1>
      <p class="text-xl max-w-2xl" style="color: #a8dbfb;">What our clients say about working with P.K. Gills Aquatics.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-8">

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
        <div class="h-1" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #0d6aae, #059669);"></div>
        <div class="p-8">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 mb-4" style="color: #d6effd;" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/>
          </svg>
          <blockquote class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed italic mb-6">
            "PK Gills has been a tremendous asset to our operation. Pat Ann is an expert in the field and her knowledge and passion for aquatics is truly unmatched. Her 30+ year track record in the industry gives us complete confidence in every delivery. We have never been disappointed — fish arrive healthy, on time, and at fair prices."
          </blockquote>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-semibold" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d6aae, #094e84);">JS</div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-semibold" style="color: #041e35;">Janet Scheffman</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">Hurricane Aquatics</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
        <div class="h-1" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #059669, #0d6aae);"></div>
        <div class="p-8">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 mb-4" style="color: #d6effd;" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/>
          </svg>
          <blockquote class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed italic mb-6">
            "Pat Ann Church is wonderful to work with. She is punctual, dependable, and her prices are very competitive. I have referred her to several clients and they have all been extremely satisfied with her services. She is the kind of business partner you can count on year after year."
          </blockquote>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-semibold" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669, #027055);">LC</div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-semibold" style="color: #041e35;">Lynn Cook, CPA</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">Client</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
        <div class="h-1" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #7c3aed, #0d6aae);"></div>
        <div class="p-8">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 mb-4" style="color: #d6effd;" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/>
          </svg>
          <blockquote class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed italic mb-6">
            "The Roosevelt Water Conservation District has been working with P.K. Gills and Pat Ann Church for a number of years. She has consistently provided quality fish stock on schedule and within budget. Her understanding of aquatic systems and Arizona's specific needs makes her an invaluable resource for our district. Her track record speaks for itself."
          </blockquote>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-semibold" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed, #5b21b6);">BS</div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-semibold" style="color: #041e35;">B. Strader, P.E.</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">Roosevelt Water Conservation District</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl p-8 text-center" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #041e35, #063356);">
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-white text-2xl mb-3">Join Our Satisfied Clients</h2>
        <p class="mb-6" style="color: #a8dbfb;">Contact us today to discuss how P.K. Gills can help with your aquatic management needs.</p>
        <a href={u("/contact")} class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-semibold text-white" style="background-color: #0d6aae;">Get in Touch</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
